      <title><![CDATA[安装 Flatpak 格式的 Deepin 应用]]></title>
      <url>/2018/install-dfpapp/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script>
    <div id="aplayer-hFbvdhUI" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker" data-id="463268241" data-server="netease" data-type="song" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="true" data-mutex="false" data-listmaxheight="340px" data-preload="none" data-theme="#3ac5bb" data-loop="none" data-volume="0.5"></div>
<p>Deepin 最近也是多灾多难，<del>老板跑路（，</del>新版本难产……</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h1 id="正文"><a href="#正文" class="headerlink" title="正文"></a>正文</h1><p>话说 Deepin 团队已经使用 <a href="https://flatpak.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Flatpak</a> 封装自家应用，这无疑极大方便了其他发行版用户。但是 Deepin 没有直接提供 Flatpak 源等等，所以想要安装还是要自己动手。</p>
<h2 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h2><ul>
<li>好一点的网络</li>
<li><a href="https://flatpak.org/setup/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">安装了 Flatpak</a> 的 Linux 发行版 (x86_64)</li>
<li>洗把脸</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="安装-Deepin-Runtime"><a href="#安装-Deepin-Runtime" class="headerlink" title="安装 Deepin Runtime"></a>安装 Deepin Runtime</h2><p>Flatpak 应用运行需要一套运行时（Runtime）作为基础环境，Freedesktop、GNOME、KDE <a href="http://docs.flatpak.org/en/latest/available-runtimes.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">都做了一套</a>供 GTK/Qt 等应用开发者选用。Deepin 则自己做了一套。</p>
<p><a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/deepin/pool/main/d/deepin-fprt-com.deepin.runtime-15.5/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载</a> <code>com.deepin.platform-15.5_1.0.4+r2_amd64.deb</code> <code>deepin-fprt-org.deepin.flatdeb.base.platform-15.5_1.0.5+r7_amd64.deb</code>，解压出打包好的 <code>bundle</code> 文件 （版本号可能不同）</p>
<p>（以下均以 TUNA 镜像源为例，官方源实在无法直视）</p>
<p><img src="https://i.jpg.dog/img/801c7d0df307487125b66dcbd954267e.png" alt="801c7d0df307487125b66dcbd954267e.png"></p>
<p>然后安装</p>
<pre class="line-numbers highlight language-base"><code class="language-base">flatpak install bundle --bundle
<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>
<h2 id="安装应用"><a href="#安装应用" class="headerlink" title="安装应用"></a>安装应用</h2><p>Deepin 打包好的应用包括：</p>
<ul>
<li>深度日历</li>
<li>深度计算器</li>
<li>深度看图</li>
<li>深度影院</li>
<li>深度音乐</li>
<li>深度录屏</li>
<li>深度录音</li>
<li>深度截图</li>
<li>还有好多……</li>
<li>我列不完了……</li>
<li>Shadowsocks-Qt5 （？？？）</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/deepin/pool/main/d/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/deepin/pool/main/d/</a></p>
<p>Ctrl + F <code>deepin-fpapp</code></p>
<p>这里以「深度日历」为例</p>
<hr>
<p><a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/deepin/pool/main/d/deepin-fpapp-org.deepin.flatdeb.deepin-calendar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载</a> <code>deepin-fpapp-org.deepin.flatdeb.deepin-calendar_1.2.3+r1_amd64.deb</code></p>
<p>依照上文，解压出 <code>bundle</code>，如法炮制</p>
<pre class="line-numbers highlight language-bash"><code class="language-bash">flatpak <span class="token function">install</span> bundle --bundle
Installing: org.deepin.flatdeb.deepin-calendar/x86_64/master from bundle bundle
Now at 38c791026f75.
<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>
<p><em><code>org.deepin.flatdeb.deepin-calendar</code> 是应用包名</em></p>
<h2 id="运行"><a href="#运行" class="headerlink" title="运行"></a>运行</h2><p>安装完的 Flatpak 应用可以通过命令行运行</p>
<pre class="line-numbers highlight language-bash"><code class="language-bash">flatpak run org.deepin.flatdeb.deepin-calendar
<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>
<p>每次都通过命令启动肯定会让人疯掉，显然需要写一个 <code>.desktop</code> 文件，或者用类似 KDE Menu Editor 这样的工具来新建一个</p>
<pre><code>[Desktop Entry]
Exec=flatpak run org.deepin.flatdeb.deepin-calendar
...
</code></pre><p>Deepin 应用的图标可以在<a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/deepin/pool/main/d/deepin-icon-theme/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>找到</p>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<p>openSUSE Tumbleweed<br>KDE Plasma 5.13.2</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/07/15/5b4b488998855.png" alt="Screenshot_20180715_211032.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>深度音乐</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.jpg.dog/img/5df278132a1b57c329b1a28f73fdcb4c.png" alt="5df278132a1b57c329b1a28f73fdcb4c.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>深度取色器 （Plasma 有更方便的 #斜眼）</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.jpg.dog/img/a33a2bb704a933eaca84a9c41604fee1.png" alt="a33a2bb704a933eaca84a9c41604fee1.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>深度日历</p>
</blockquote>
<p>……</p>
<h1 id="附"><a href="#附" class="headerlink" title="附"></a>附</h1><ul>
<li>Deepin 提到未来可能会建立 Flatpak 源，显然这又是一大张饼（</li>
<li>我曾考虑过在 <a href="https://flathub.org/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Flathub</a> 上打包一些 Deepin 应用，但 Flathub 原则上只允许开发者本人来维护……</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
      
