      <title><![CDATA[一些古董 Linux 发行版们 Vol. 1]]></title>
      <url>/2018/some-antique-linux-vol1/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script><p>上个月突然心血来潮，，从 1 月 27 号开始陆续挖了一些古董级 Linux 发行版出来考古。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><em>其实还不算古董，真的古董不是还没去挖就是恐怕连尸块都找不着了……</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p>现在把这次考古的部分内容整理出来，大概只有我这种闲人会干这种事。</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h1 id="正文"><a href="#正文" class="headerlink" title="正文"></a>正文</h1><p>本次考古：</p>
<ul>
<li>Linux Deepin 9.12 </li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p>Hiweed 就属于那种尸块都找不着的……</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><p>Fedora 7 </p>
</li>
<li><p>Debian 1.3.1</p>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p>Debian 1.1 手头倒也有，不过 QEMU 我不太会用</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>Red Hat Linux 9</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="关于主机"><a href="#关于主机" class="headerlink" title="关于主机"></a>关于主机</h2><p>Manjaro / Deepin DE，使用 VirtualBox。配置稀烂不详列。</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a783f2ce9354.png" alt="深度截图_20180127190310.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>有多烂呢，就是这么烂的……</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Linux-Deepin-9-12"><a href="#Linux-Deepin-9-12" class="headerlink" title="Linux Deepin 9.12"></a>Linux Deepin 9.12</h2><p>来源：<a href="http://cdimage.deepin.com/releases-archive/9.12/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deepin 官方归档</a><br><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a78409671628.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180127184429.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7840a09f69f.png" alt="深度截图_20180127184500.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7840a2d4e7d.png" alt="深度截图_20180127184544.png"> </p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7841d32b573.png" alt="VirtualBox_Linux Deepin_27_01_2018_18_53_20.png"> </p>
<blockquote>
<p>此时 Deepin 仍基于 Ubuntu ，配 Xfce4</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7842dd8f524.png" alt="VirtualBox_Linux Deepin_27_01_2018_18_59_13.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>安装完成</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a784365e8bb5.png" alt="VirtualBox_Linux Deepin_27_01_2018_19_14_57.png"> </p>
<blockquote>
<p>WebQQ 的凝视</p>
<p>腾讯曾于 2008 年发布 QQ for Linux，不过不久后便被放弃</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7844fee593a.png" alt="VirtualBox_Linux Deepin_27_01_2018_19_36_56.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>预装了 Wine 全套，显然是为从 Windows 过渡准备的——Deepin 的这一点到今天都没变</p>
<p>然后 Deepin 就踏上了倒腾 Wine 的不归路……</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7845a6d5524.png" alt="VirtualBox_Linux Deepin_27_01_2018_19_27_48.png"></p>
<hr>
<p>Hiweed 作为国内最早的社区发行版之一，在十多年前的蛮荒时代难得有完善的中文化。看看今天 StartOS 死、红旗绝，只剩下深之度活了下来……</p>
<p><em>另：启动任何程序都奇慢无比，不知是不是个别问题</em></p>
<h2 id="Debian-1-3-1"><a href="#Debian-1-3-1" class="headerlink" title="Debian 1.3.1"></a>Debian 1.3.1</h2><p>来源：<a href="https://github.com/rdebath/debian-bo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></p>
<p>（需要使用  <code>jigdo</code>  下载 / 或者说生成镜像）</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a784963f1e17.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180203131609.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7849654c5bd.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180203131716.png"> </p>
<blockquote>
<p>安装步骤一览……</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a784964e76d8.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180203131814.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>现在我都经常用的 cfdisk</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7849652e6ba.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180203132738.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>ext2 格盘中……</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a784964adbc0.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180203134321.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a784abec9f23.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180203134441.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>从“光驱”安装内核和基本系统</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a784b10819ca.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180203135402.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>那年头网络不发达，DNS 也要手动设置一下</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a784b9e1dc10.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180203135757.png"> </p>
<blockquote>
<p>Booting with LILO…</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a784b9e85e39.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180203135926.png"> </p>
<blockquote>
<p>像是账户这些次要的配置，是在安装完成后设置的</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<p>离开地球表面前往更高维度空间的 Ian Murdock 当初不会想到 Debian 现在会有……</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a784e8545b75.png" alt="Screenshot_20180205-202918.png"></p>
<p>……如此恐怖的<a href="https://github.com/fabiololix/linuxtimeline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">时间线图</a></p>
<h2 id="Red-Hat-Linux-9"><a href="#Red-Hat-Linux-9" class="headerlink" title="Red Hat Linux 9"></a>Red Hat Linux 9</h2><p>来源：<a href="https://archive.org/details/redhat-9.0_release" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Archive.org</a></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a78521b13b91.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180128152544.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a78521f301e3.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180128152707.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a78521db698a.png" alt="VirtualBox_Red Hat 9_28_01_2018_15_28_00.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a78521deef8e.png" alt="VirtualBox_Red Hat 9_28_01_2018_15_34_37.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7852db984fe.png" alt="VirtualBox_Red Hat 9_28_01_2018_15_38_14.png"> </p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a78521c6ca26.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180128153829.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>轶闻………</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a78521f67d80.png" alt="VirtualBox_Red Hat 9_28_01_2018_15_40_19.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>总共三张盘，塞了一堆软件</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a78521c83b9c.png" alt="VirtualBox_Red Hat 9_28_01_2018_15_52_09.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7853be35eb6.png" alt="VirtualBox_Red Hat 9_28_01_2018_15_53_44.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>X 没出来？<strong>不要在意这些细节……</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<p>之所以选择 Red Hat Linux 9 而不是更早的版本，因为 Red Hat 9 影响力大到成了一个梗——用来嘲笑被同样古董的教材坑害的小白。</p>
<p>Red Hat 9 之后，RHEL 和 Fedora Core 一分为二。</p>
<h2 id="Fedora-7"><a href="#Fedora-7" class="headerlink" title="Fedora 7"></a>Fedora 7</h2><p>来源：<a href="http://archives.fedoraproject.org/pub/archive/fedora/linux/releases/7/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fedora 官方归档</a></p>
<p><em>不要问我为什么不用 Fedora Core </em></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7855d4b5559.png" alt="深度截图_选择区域_20180128103053.png"> </p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7855d6ac9ea.png" alt="VirtualBox_Fedora 7_28_01_2018_10_33_21.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7855d5c6a59.png" alt="VirtualBox_Fedora 7_28_01_2018_10_52_27.png"> </p>
<blockquote>
<p>安装过程与 Red Hat 9 大致相同，略过。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a785686b3c82.png" alt="VirtualBox_Fedora 7_28_01_2018_10_54_01.png"> </p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a785686b5c10.png" alt="VirtualBox_Fedora 7_28_01_2018_10_54_17.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>启动中……</p>
<p>此时我的表情只有</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7860e95049a.png" alt="IMG_20180205_210614.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7857f90dc32.png" alt="VirtualBox_Fedora 7_28_01_2018_10_56_31.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>同样是在安装完成后再进行细节配置</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7857fb5ff1e.png" alt="VirtualBox_Fedora 7_28_01_2018_11_02_48.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>GNOME 2.18 的凝视</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7857f991a26.png" alt="VirtualBox_Fedora 7_28_01_2018_11_05_11.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>“万恶之源”般的 SELinux</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/02/05/5a7857fb6387e.png" alt="VirtualBox_Fedora 7_28_01_2018_11_13_45.png"> </p>
<hr>
<p>一转眼也十多年了，Fedora 也给 RHEL 当了十多年白老鼠了……</p>
<h1 id="结"><a href="#结" class="headerlink" title="结"></a>结</h1><p>许多老古董比我都不知道老到哪里去，而我在 2016 年才开始接触 Linux 。</p>
<p>虽说翻古董怀旧怀旧大概只有我这种闲人会这么干，不过却也倒有些乐趣。</p>
<hr>
<p><strong>Vol. 2 预订名单</strong></p>
<p><em>更新时间：？？？</em></p>
<ul>
<li><p>Ubuntu <em>（未完成）</em></p>
</li>
<li><p>Mandrake / Mandriva <em>（未完成）</em></p>
